songs.title: Royce Outro
songs.lyrics:
Yo on behalf on myself, Mike B, Kino, my nigga Green Lantern, my nigga pro, my nigga Kid Vishis, my nigga Sucka Free, my nigga Junes Flow
Oh, I want to thank everybody that participated in the project, too
And uhm... I know I say a lot of crazy ass shit, half the time I just be playin' man, so
If I brought your name up or summin an' you ain't like it *laughing*
All you gotta do man it's when you see me you know just let me know how you feelin' you know what I'm sayin'
It ain't no big deal man you know I'll apologize to you or I might just tell you to stop acting like a little baby
*stop acting like a little baby (in the background)*
Don't act like such a little baby
I'm the shit fool
